messages.messageBody:
<<Not the breed but the psycho part>>

It is funny because I love her to death but she has a tendency to bark at
particular places in the floor where nothing can be detected by humans, she
tends to forget that her brother is "pack leader", she went through a period
where she thought I was going to take her food away and would growl at me.
But most of the time she is fine.

Our 4-H group is doing a dog training project this year and is bringing in a
professional trainer to work with the kids. I hope it helps.

Julie
